<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27Jan1930"><font color="red">27 January 1930</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Stuart Gilbert): First, about Mr J&apos;s sight &mdash; the &lsquo;good&rsquo; eye is still inadequate for reading; but, strangely enough, the other is slowly coming into action &hellip; I think there is hope that in time he may be able to read with it &hellip; Meanwhile Mr J is spending busy days &mdash; launchina an opera singer! &hellip; For the time being Work in Progress does not progress but I hope Mr Joyce will soon have launched his singer at Covent Garden or the Metropole and return to H.C.E. and Missisliffi! </div>
